s of the story.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 28. Feb 2023) 0aAuthorsvFiction. 0aFiction. 4aFiction & Short Stories. 7aLITERARY CRITICISM / General.2bisacsh1 aWilson, Michael K., econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aWilson, Michiko N., econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertCornell University Press Archive Pre-2000z978311053617140uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/978194224260440uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9781942242604423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9781942242604/original  a978-3-11-053617-1  Cornell University Press Archive Pre-2000b2000  aEBA_BACKALL  aEBA_CL_LT  aEBA_EBACKALL  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_ECL_LT  aEBA_EEBKALL  aEBA_ESSHALL  aEBA_PPALL  aEBA_SSHALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aPDA11SSHE  aPDA13ENGE  aPDA17SSHEE  aPDA5EBK